OL,3,CGerry Adams 'major, major player in
OL,4,Cwar', High Court told
OL,6,FGerry Adams was a "major, major player
OL,7,Fin the war", according to one of his
OL,8,Fformer friends who was an IRA
OL,9,Fvolunteer, the High Court has heard.
OL,11,FBrendan Hughes said the words during a
OL,12,Frecorded interview that was played in
OL,13,Fcourt to Mr Adams, who is giving
OL,14,Fevidence in defence of a legal claim
OL,15,Fbrought against him by three victims
OL,16,Fof bombings in England by the
OL,17,FProvisional IRA in the 1970s and 1990s.
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@KO]
