OL,3,CGerry Adams 'major, major player in
OL,4,Cwar', High Court told
OL,6,FThe former Sinn Fein president denies
OL,7,Fthe allegations and is defending the
OL,8,Fclaim, telling the court that he had
OL,9,F"no involvement whatsoever" in the
OL,10,Fbombings and was never a member of the
OL,11,FProvisional IRA.
OL,13,FMr Hughes and Mr Adams were at Long
OL,14,FKesh prison together in the early
OL,15,F1970s and they were together the day
OL,16,Fbefore Mr Hughes died in 2008, the
OL,17,Fcourt heard.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
