OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773867709
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'major, major player in
OL,4,Cwar', High Court told
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, after playing the clip
OL,7,Fin which Mr Hughes calls Mr Adams a
OL,8,Fmajor player, Sir Max Hill KC, for the
OL,9,Fthree bombing victims, said: "You
OL,10,Fwere, weren't you Mr Adams? And you
OL,11,Fdeny it."
OL,13,FMr Adams said: "I was president of
OL,14,FSinn Fein for 35 years, deeply
OL,15,Finvolved in the struggle.
OL,17,F"I defended the use of armed struggle
OL,18,Fwhen I thought it was appropriate.
OL,26,@qD@^OUsD@IO]uD@POUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
