PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773867709
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'major, major player in
OL,4,Cwar', High Court told
OL,6,F"I'm not boasting but I don't deny
OL,7,Fthat I was a person of interest, of
OL,8,Finfluence, and I used that influence
OL,9,Fas best I could to move from war to
OL,10,Fpeace and that is, thankfully, what we
OL,11,Fare enjoying to this day."
OL,13,FSir Max also quoted a passage from the
OL,14,Fbook Say Nothing, in which Mr Hughes
OL,15,Fgave an interview saying that Mr
OL,16,FAdams's IRA membership was common
OL,17,Fknowledge.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
