OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773867709
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'major, major player in
OL,4,Cwar', High Court told
OL,6,FHe said: "'The British know it. The
OL,7,Fpeople on the street know it. The dogs
OL,8,Fknow it on the street. And he's
OL,9,Fstanding there denying it'."
OL,11,FSir Max also described Mr Hughes as a
OL,12,F"proud IRA volunteer until his death".
OL,14,FMr Adams replied: "I don't know what
OL,15,Fhis status was.
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@\O]tD@AOUtD@eO]vD@SOU
