OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773867709
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'major, major player in
OL,4,Cwar', High Court told
OL,6,F"It's interesting that the direction
OL,7,Ffrom the claimants' counsel was that I
OL,8,Fwas helping, involved, in those armed
OL,9,Factions and those decisions to bring
OL,10,Fthe war to Britain, while those who
OL,11,Fwere against what we were doing saw us
OL,12,Fas traitors."
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, Mr Adams told the court
OL,15,Fthat while he did not distance himself
OL,16,Ffrom the Provisional IRA, he was glad
OL,17,Fthe organisation had "left the stage"
OL,18,Fand that there were "dastardly things
OL,19,Fthat were done that should never have
OL,20,Fbeen done".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@MO]yD@VOUyD@eO]zD@UOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
