OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773867709
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'major, major player in
OL,4,Cwar', High Court told
OL,6,FIn his witness statement, he also said
OL,7,Fthat he "had no involvement in or
OL,8,Fadvance knowledge" of the three
OL,9,Fbombings.
OL,11,FAnne Studd KC, for the bomb victims,
OL,12,Fpreviously told the trial that being a
OL,13,Fmember of Sinn Fein and a member of
OL,14,Fthe Provisional IRA was "a distinction
OL,15,Fwithout a difference" for some
OL,16,Findividuals, including Mr Adams.
OL,18,FMs Studd also told the court that Mr
OL,19,FAdams had "a foot in each camp" of the
OL,20,Fmilitary and political sides of the
OL,21,FIrish Republican movement.
OL,26,@oD@IOUpD@RO]vD@YOUwD@UO]{D@KOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
