OL,3,CGerry Adams 'major, major player in
OL,4,Cwar', High Court told
OL,6,FThe barrister continued that Mr Adams
OL,7,Fwas "directly responsible for and
OL,8,Fcomplicit in those decisions made by
OL,9,Fthat organisation to detonate bombs on
OL,10,Fthe British mainland in 1973 and 1996".
OL,12,FThe trial before Mr Justice Swift is
OL,13,Fexpected to end later in March.
